# BROWSER-replies.md - Notifications Page Reply Patterns

**Notifications URL:** `https://bsky.app/notifications`
**Page test ID:** `data-testid="notifsFeed"` — container for notification items.

## S 1. Extract Unreplied Posts (Notifications Page)

Navigate to `https://bsky.app/notifications`, then extract with 3s embedded wait.

On Bluesky, notification items contain links to posts. Each notification is inside a `div[role="link"]` container.

```javascript
browser.act({
  kind: "evaluate",
  fn: `async () => {
    await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 3000));
    const containers = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('div[role="link"]'));
    const results = [];
    const seen = new Set();

    for (const container of containers) {
      if (results.length >= 10) break;
      const link = container.querySelector('a[href*="/post/"]');
      if (!link) continue;

      const urlMatch = link.href.match(/\\/post\\/([^/?]+)/);
      if (!urlMatch) continue;
      const postId = urlMatch[1];
      if (seen.has(postId)) continue;
      seen.add(postId);

      const text = container.innerText;
      const lines = text.split('\\n').filter(l => l.trim());

      // Skip our own posts
      if (text.includes('{{handle}}')) continue;

      // Check if already replied (look for reply count indicator)
      const replyBtn = container.querySelector('button[aria-label*="Reply"]');
      const replyLabel = replyBtn ? replyBtn.getAttribute('aria-label') : '';
      const replyCount = parseInt((replyLabel.match(/(\\d+)\\s*repl/i) || [])[1]) || 0;

      results.push({
        url: link.href,
        postId: postId,
        author: lines[0] || 'unknown',
        preview: lines.slice(1).join(' ').slice(0, 200),
        replyCount
      });
    }
    return results;
  }`,
  profile: "{{browser_profile}}"
})
```

