## S 2. Open Reply Dialog on Notification Post

**Requires `allowedIds`** — array of post IDs from grep pre-check (step 3b).

Navigate to the post URL, then use S 4b (Compose reply click) + S 5 (type and submit).

On Bluesky notifications page, clicking a notification navigates to the post page directly. From there, use the standard compose reply flow:

1. Navigate to post URL
2. Run BROWSER-engage.md S 4b (click "Compose reply")
3. Run BROWSER-core.md S 5 (type + submit)

This is different from Threads where replies happen via popup from activity page. On Bluesky, always navigate to the post page first.
